<p>If you are still unsure what Pragmata is actually about, it's Capcom's all-new sci-fi action adventure which comes with a "unique hacking twist". The game's two protagonists are Hugh and Diana, who while at first glance may seem to be just a young, bright-eyed girl, is in fact an android. The duo must work together to survive, with each bringing their own different skills to the table.</p>
<p>"The result is a fascinating mix that was only better in its more difficult and more thought-provoking proper hands-on than it was in the two previous proof-of-concept style demos," Alex Donaldson wrote in <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/pragmatas-unique-action-and-puzzle-blend-may-grab-the-headlines-but-as-its-creators-explain-its-secret-sauce-is-all-about-rhythm-1">Eurogamer's Pragmata preview</a>.</p>
