<!-- code from Primis -->
<p>Pragmata was once <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/capcoms-next-gen-project-pragamata-wont-launch-until-2022">planned for a 2022 release</a>, having been originally revealed in 2020. It is slated to release across PS5, Xbox Series X/S, PC, and <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Nintendo Switch 2</a>. If you are keen for more before then, though, there is <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3357650/PRAGMATA/">currently a demo for Pragmata available on Steam</a>.</p>

